1254
00:39:22,059 --> 00:39:22,780
[SPEAKER_01] a s druge strane,

1255
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:24,320
[SPEAKER_01] neovisno o nama,

1256
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] dijeluju sestre koje imaju svoju strukturu

1257
00:39:26,539 --> 00:39:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] poput provincije,

1258
00:39:27,659 --> 00:39:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno kao što je uobičajeno u crkvi,

1259
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali javno vjerničko društvo je

1260
00:39:34,119 --> 00:39:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] kao prijelazna faza prema onome,

1261
00:39:36,239 --> 00:39:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] prema razvoju redovničke zajednice,

1262
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači tu su aktivne sestre

1263
00:39:41,699 --> 00:39:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] i kontemplativne sestre,

1264
00:39:43,159 --> 00:39:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] njih oko 50-ak,

1265
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji isto, ovaj,

1266
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:49,480
[SPEAKER_01] dijeluju u različitim biskupijama,

1267
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] u različitim službama,

1268
00:39:50,719 --> 00:39:53,699
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo, ne znam,

1269
00:39:53,699 --> 00:39:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] od toga da su,

1270
00:39:55,199 --> 00:39:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] da rade u karitasima,

1271
00:39:56,980 --> 00:39:57,699
[SPEAKER_01] hospicijima,

1272
00:39:57,699 --> 00:40:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] rade u župnome pastoralu,

1273
00:40:00,699 --> 00:40:02,860
[SPEAKER_01] rade u,

1274
00:40:04,179 --> 00:40:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se pojavi potreba,

1275
00:40:06,199 --> 00:40:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] znači na usluzi su,

1276
00:40:08,039 --> 00:40:10,719
[SPEAKER_01] evo, skrbe za umirovljene biskupe,

1277
00:40:10,719 --> 00:40:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] za dva umirovljena biskupa,

1278
00:40:12,219 --> 00:40:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] i tako, evo,

1279
00:40:14,780 --> 00:40:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se pojavi pastoralna potreba,

1280
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,860
[SPEAKER_01] koja je sukladna na našoj karizmi,

1281
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj sestre,

1282
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] sestre se uključuju.

1283
00:40:23,219 --> 00:40:24,539
[SPEAKER_02] Kad je izrašla ova informacija

1284
00:40:24,539 --> 00:40:26,239
[SPEAKER_02] u petak o uhičenju,

1285
00:40:26,239 --> 00:40:27,639
[SPEAKER_02] onda se nekako steko dojam

1286
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:28,320
[SPEAKER_02] da ste vi neka,

1287
00:40:28,320 --> 00:40:30,480
[SPEAKER_02] ono, ilegalna zajednica u crkvi,

1288
00:40:30,480 --> 00:40:32,440
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo u nekoj sivoj zoni,

1289
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,039
[SPEAKER_02] i da,

1290
00:40:33,039 --> 00:40:34,480
[SPEAKER_02] neki mračnjaci,

1291
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,920
[SPEAKER_02] za koji se ne zna što radi,

1292
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,380
[SPEAKER_02] zato sam vas zapravo izvao

1293
00:40:37,380 --> 00:40:38,320
[SPEAKER_02] da se, ono, vidi,

1294
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,760
[SPEAKER_02] da se dozna istina ta o društvu,

1295
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,360
[SPEAKER_02] ovlija deo.

1296
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:44,199
[SPEAKER_02] Koji je vaš službeni neki crkvenist?

1297
00:40:44,199 --> 00:40:45,019
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, kad smo kod častnice,

1298
00:40:45,019 --> 00:40:45,760
[SPEAKER_02] sad samo da završim.

1299
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:46,900
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, da je sve ok.

1300
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,820
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, ja sam čuvao kod redovnica,

1301
00:40:48,820 --> 00:40:49,599
[SPEAKER_02] znali su mi reći,

1302
00:40:49,599 --> 00:40:50,840
[SPEAKER_02] one nisu prave redovnice,

1303
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:52,659
[SPEAKER_02] one nemaju zapravo redovničke zavijete,

1304
00:40:52,659 --> 00:40:54,880
[SPEAKER_02] ali oni nisu redovnička zajednica.

1305
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,699
[SPEAKER_02] Ali imamo da se taj partijeljstvom misle

1306
00:40:56,699 --> 00:40:57,539
[SPEAKER_02] o iste pravni.

1307
00:40:57,539 --> 00:40:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da, o čemu se darko radi,

1308
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi jednostavno ne razumiju

1309
00:41:02,239 --> 00:41:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] redovnička zajednica,

1310
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] ili bilo koja zajednica posvećenog života

1311
00:41:07,099 --> 00:41:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne nastaje preko noći.

1312
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može neko uzeti sad

1313
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] i reći, ja želim biti redovnica,

1314
00:41:13,539 --> 00:41:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] i sad će odmah crkva reći,

1315
00:41:15,639 --> 00:41:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ti si redovnica.

1316
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nego nastanak zajednica ima svoje faze.

1317
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo, znači, naša zajednica,

1318
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] jel, ovnija deo koja se sastoji

1319
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] od dva krila, krila braća i sestara,

1320
00:41:30,380 --> 00:41:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji su, znači, članovi u biti zajednica,

1321
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] ostalo su lajičke obitelji,

1322
00:41:36,239 --> 00:41:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji su više prijatelji,

1323
00:41:37,719 --> 00:41:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] molitveni, molitvena podrška,

1324
00:41:40,579 --> 00:41:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] dok se to, jel, ne strukturira.

1325
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo zbog toga što se zajednica

1326
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] nalazi u tom nastanku,

1327
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve je napravljeno po svim,

1328
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači, zakonskim propisima

1329
00:41:51,179 --> 00:41:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] katoličke crkve

1330
00:41:52,599 --> 00:41:54,179
[SPEAKER_00] i u suradnje s biskupima.

1331
00:41:54,179 --> 00:41:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedan korak nije napravljen bez toga.

1332
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] A što kaže praksa, recimo,

1333
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] crkvena u nastanku tih zajednica,

1334
00:42:01,219 --> 00:42:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno,

1335
00:42:02,719 --> 00:42:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] redovničkih zajednica,

1336
00:42:06,719 --> 00:42:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] one koje idu prema tome putu

1337
00:42:08,699 --> 00:42:09,719
[SPEAKER_00] da budu ustanove,

1338
00:42:09,719 --> 00:42:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] da budu samostalne na neki način,

1339
00:42:11,840 --> 00:42:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] karizme koje će unutar crkve

1340
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] dobiti svoju strukturu.

1341
00:42:15,860 --> 00:42:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što je rekao Don Giuliano,

1342
00:42:19,019 --> 00:42:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] jedne provincije,

1343
00:42:20,619 --> 00:42:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] imamo Isusovce,

1344
00:42:22,199 --> 00:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Salesijance,

1345
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] razne te crkvene zajednice,

1346
00:42:27,159 --> 00:42:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] koje su isto tako nastale

1347
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom povijesnom trenutku crkve.

1348
00:42:31,659 --> 00:42:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Što je važno,

1349
00:42:32,539 --> 00:42:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači zajednica u tom svom prvom dijelu

1350
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] 2003. ženska, 2005. muška,

1351
00:42:41,579 --> 00:42:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] ima taj svoj korijen

1352
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] u molitvenoj zajednice

1353
00:42:45,099 --> 00:42:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji su započeli Don Jospi,

1354
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] majka Jozefina, 1998.

1355
00:42:49,039 --> 00:42:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ono su to počeli

1356
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] čisto da prodube molitveni života,

1357
00:42:54,659 --> 00:42:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] kao jedna zajednica molitve i slično.

1358
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

1359
00:43:00,179 --> 00:43:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] kada, budući da su i vi sami znate

1360
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao lajk,

1361
00:43:03,880 --> 00:43:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] da su ljudi žedni, gladni,

1362
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] traže,

1363
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] tako upravo se dogodilo je

1364
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] s našom zajednicom.

1365
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi koji su ih upoznavali,

1366
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] željeli su nalaziti se,

1367
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] dolaziti,

1368
00:43:15,360 --> 00:43:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] hodočastiti i tako dalje.

1369
00:43:18,619 --> 00:43:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] I tu, znači,

1370
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] ono što poštuje

1371
00:43:22,159 --> 00:43:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] naravni taj princip

1372
00:43:24,380 --> 00:43:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] ljudskog udruživanja,

1373
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] poštuje sama crkva

1374
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] i zato je kanonskim zakonnikom

1375
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] dozvolila,

1376
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] znači, to pravo na udruživanje

1377
00:43:33,019 --> 00:43:34,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje imamo krštenjem

1378
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj katoličkoj crkvi

1379
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] po zakonu,

1380
00:43:38,139 --> 00:43:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] a za svećenike

1381
00:43:39,900 --> 00:43:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] i one koji žele ići

1382
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] putem posvećenog života

1383
00:43:43,460 --> 00:43:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili redovničkog,

1384
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] to je i preporučeno

1385
00:43:45,659 --> 00:43:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] da crkva i prepoznaje

1386
00:43:48,099 --> 00:43:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] i razlučuje

1387
00:43:49,239 --> 00:43:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] i podupire.

1388
00:43:50,380 --> 00:43:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] I što je se dogodilo?

1389
00:43:52,039 --> 00:43:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se oko Don Josipa

1390
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] okupljao sve veći broj

1391
00:43:56,019 --> 00:43:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] mladih koji su, evo,

1392
00:43:57,679 --> 00:43:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] Don Julijano je bio

1393
00:43:59,119 --> 00:44:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji student

1394
00:44:00,019 --> 00:44:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] u Rijeci medicine,

1395
00:44:01,119 --> 00:44:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] primio nagradu dekana,

1396
00:44:03,659 --> 00:44:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji student u Splitu,

1397
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] promišljao je o ovom,

1398
00:44:07,940 --> 00:44:09,780
[SPEAKER_00] onom, razne specializacije,

1399
00:44:10,420 --> 00:44:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] ostavio je sve,

1400
00:44:11,460 --> 00:44:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] krenuo s Don Josipom

1401
00:44:13,519 --> 00:44:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno sa drugom braćom,

1402
00:44:14,940 --> 00:44:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] još jednim liječnikom,

1403
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] jednim zubnim tehničarom,

1404
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači to su razna zanimanja

1405
00:44:21,059 --> 00:44:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja se nikad ne bi našla.

1406
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] Biskup koji je to prepoznao,

1407
00:44:25,019 --> 00:44:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] dao je dozvolu,

1408
00:44:26,199 --> 00:44:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] pozvo je, evo,

1409
00:44:27,460 --> 00:44:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] možete biti s njim,

1410
00:44:28,820 --> 00:44:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljate o pozivu,

1411
00:44:30,880 --> 00:44:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] uključit ćete se u bogosloviju

1412
00:44:32,800 --> 00:44:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] i tako iz jedne faze,

1413
00:44:34,739 --> 00:44:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] možemo reći,

1414
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] zajedništva de facto,

1415
00:44:37,500 --> 00:44:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] potpuno legitimnog

1416
00:44:39,199 --> 00:44:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] i preporučenog od crkve.

1417
00:44:41,579 --> 00:44:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je u jednom trenutku,

1418
00:44:43,760 --> 00:44:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to raslo,

1419
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] i među djevojkama

1420
00:44:47,239 --> 00:44:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] koje se odlučile

1421
00:44:48,199 --> 00:44:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] za posvećeni život,

1422
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] i među mladićima,

1423
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] u osobi nadbiskupa Ivana Dejučića

1424
00:44:55,460 --> 00:44:56,820
[SPEAKER_00] odlučila dati tome

1425
00:44:56,820 --> 00:44:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] jednu pravnu strukturu.

1426
00:44:58,500 --> 00:44:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1427
00:44:59,360 --> 00:45:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kad imate,

1428
00:45:00,980 --> 00:45:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] već je tad bilo oko

1429
00:45:02,539 --> 00:45:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] dvadesetak sestara,

1430
00:45:05,099 --> 00:45:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] oko 15-16 svećenika,

1431
00:45:08,480 --> 00:45:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] braće,

1432
00:45:08,980 --> 00:45:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] nadbiskup je razmišljao

1433
00:45:11,360 --> 00:45:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je šteta,

1434
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] vidi da to privlači mlade,

1435
00:45:14,539 --> 00:45:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] vidi da ima

1436
00:45:17,400 --> 00:45:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslovljene,

1437
00:45:19,300 --> 00:45:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] blagotvorne,

1438
00:45:20,900 --> 00:45:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] blagotvoran jako utjecaj

1439
00:45:22,860 --> 00:45:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] na pastoral,

1440
00:45:23,719 --> 00:45:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] na služenje,

1441
00:45:24,820 --> 00:45:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] na odgovor na potrebe ljudi

1442
00:45:27,159 --> 00:45:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] u vremenu u kojem živimo.

1443
00:45:29,280 --> 00:45:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] On je savjetovao se

1444
00:45:31,059 --> 00:45:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] sa raznim stručnjacima

1445
00:45:33,400 --> 00:45:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče toga

1446
00:45:34,599 --> 00:45:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] i odlučio,

1447
00:45:35,940 --> 00:45:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

1448
00:45:36,619 --> 00:45:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] osnovati jednim dekretom

1449
00:45:39,699 --> 00:45:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] javno-vjeničko društvo

1450
00:45:41,639 --> 00:45:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] s ciljem da postane

1451
00:45:43,780 --> 00:45:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] ustanova posvećenog života.

1452
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] Što to znači?

1453
00:45:47,420 --> 00:45:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Javno-vjeničko društvo,

1454
00:45:48,599 --> 00:45:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao takvo,

1455
00:45:49,579 --> 00:45:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] ono je,

1456
00:45:50,880 --> 00:45:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

